       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. MODERNIZATION-POSTURE.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 CITIZEN-IMPACT              PIC 9(03) VALUE 094.
       01 BATCH-WINDOW-HOURS          PIC 9(03) VALUE 016.
       01 DEFECT-BACKLOG              PIC 9(03) VALUE 021.
       01 AUDIT-GAPS                  PIC 9(03) VALUE 007.
       01 INTERFACE-COUNT             PIC 9(03) VALUE 014.
       01 MODERNIZATION-RISK-SCORE    PIC 9(03) VALUE 000.
       01 MODERNIZATION-POSTURE       PIC X(08) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           COMPUTE MODERNIZATION-RISK-SCORE =
               (CITIZEN-IMPACT * 0.24)
             + (BATCH-WINDOW-HOURS * 2.1)
             + (DEFECT-BACKLOG * 1.35)
             + (AUDIT-GAPS * 5.4)
             + (INTERFACE-COUNT * 2.2).
           IF MODERNIZATION-RISK-SCORE >= 72
              MOVE "URGENT" TO MODERNIZATION-POSTURE
           ELSE
              MOVE "SEQUENCE" TO MODERNIZATION-POSTURE
           END-IF.
           DISPLAY "SYSTEM=BENEFITS-ELIGIBILITY-MAINFRAME".
           DISPLAY "POSTURE=" MODERNIZATION-POSTURE.
           STOP RUN.
